OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy day, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain developing at times
OL,7,Fthis morning, especially in the
OL,8,Fnorthwest. The rain will fizzle out
OL,9,Ffor the afternoon. Light winds, though
OL,10,Ffeeling colder than Thursday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fthis evening and overnight, with the
OL,14,Frisk of patchy rain at times. Turning
OL,15,Fchilly where any cloud breaks do
OL,16,Foccur, with a few fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,169,160,301,260,100,100
