OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FThere will still be a lot of
OL,6,Fcloud around on Saturday with further
OL,7,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,8,Frain. The wind will remain light, and
OL,9,Ffeeling a little milder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FThe
OL,12,Fcloudy theme will continue. It will be
OL,13,Fmostly dry, but some showery rain may
OL,14,Fbe possible at times. Feeling mild
OL,15,Fwhere the cloud breaks and the sun
OL,16,Fcomes out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
